12 – Rest Operator
Topics Learned
Rest Operator (...)
Function parameters
Collecting multiple values
What is Rest Operator?

Rest operator collects multiple values into an array.

Function Example
function add(...numbers) {
    console.log(numbers);
}

add(1, 2, 3, 4);
Sum Example
function add(...numbers) {
    let sum = 0;

    for (let num of numbers) {
        sum += num;
    }

    console.log(sum);
}

add(1, 2, 3, 4);
With Parameters
function show(name, ...hobbies) {
    console.log(name);
    console.log(hobbies);
}

show("Atharv", "Coding", "Gaming");
Key Takeaways
Collects values
Must be last parameter
Used in functions
